{"tid":2408226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大穆斯林學生會前副主席：我驕傲我是中國人！","createTime":"2021-02-14T17:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T17:17:34.000Z","uid":334191,"like":2,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f59dc65f3e6fb7fc23cc30a397e5807ad6482f56","tid":2408226,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T17:39:00.000Z","msg":"馬沛聰(Isa Ma) 是蘭州人，回族，在港大就讀期間曾擔任穆斯林學生會副主席，畢業後留港從事教職。他有一個頗受歡迎的YouTube頻道，用英語講解伊斯蘭，並介紹&ldquo;中國穆斯林&rdquo;所享有的&ldquo;自由生活&rdquo;。他曾向國保（政治警察）提出：願意充當黨和政府與穆斯林群眾之間的橋梁。<br />\n<br />\n不久前他對McMaster大學學生視頻演講，講完了以後，對方提出的唯一問題是：你對維吾爾人的境況怎麽看？他回答說：中國政府擔心維吾爾人分裂國家是有道理的，請不要偏聽偏信西方媒體的報道。他把這段回答截取下來作為一段小視頻发到YouTube, 並禁止評論 (鏈接1）。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我驕傲我是穆斯林，我驕傲我是中國人&rdquo;，這是他幾天前制作的新視頻（鏈接2）。我在推特質疑說：伊斯蘭當然不禁止穆斯林愛中國，正如猶太教也不禁止猶太人愛德國，你這段論證怎麽這麽像希特勒治下的&ldquo;驕傲的德國猶太人&rdquo;呢？這時发現他在幾分鐘之前已經把我拉黑了。 <br />\n鏈接1： <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6si-dE5N9TY&amp;ab_channel=IsaMa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6si-dE5N9TY%26ab_channel%3DIsaMa&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eYD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=f84bdfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6si-dE5N9TY&amp;ab_channel=IsaMa</a><br />\n鏈接2： <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kI2iiXImi3U&amp;ab_channel=IsaMa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkI2iiXImi3U%26ab_channel%3DIsaMa&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eYD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=f3a8e9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kI2iiXImi3U&amp;ab_channel=IsaMa</a>"},{"pid":"94324cfad2c6cf862b8bda1f04c2468e8f1ab4b2","tid":2408226,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"874a5744e41d08d5d327db5994789d8da760d104","tid":2408226,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T17:39:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1ba61a658b6910b2de892a5a822fc6ea1215f36","tid":